channel.title: Help with colors and login music?
channel.description:
Hello Moparscape!
I was wondering if somebody could help me with 2 problems while trying to fix up this Source and Client that is based on Rs317.
This is my first problem, when logging in the colors don't display and just give me codes:
[URL=http://imageshack.us/photo/my-images/407/helpkp.png/][IMG]http://img407.imageshack.us/img407/7122/helpkp.png[/img][/URL]
Uploaded with [URL=http://imageshack.us]ImageShack.us[/URL]
My second problem is when on the login screen I don't hear the music? This is included in the Cache but it isn't playing.
[URL=http://imageshack.us/photo/my-images/838/help1j.png/][IMG]http://img838.imageshack.us/img838/4123/help1j.png[/img][/URL]
Uploaded with [URL=http://imageshack.us]ImageShack.us[/URL]
[URL=http://imageshack.us/photo/my-images/846/help3g.png/][IMG]http://img846.imageshack.us/img846/5723/help3g.png[/img][/URL]
Uploaded with [URL=http://imageshack.us]ImageShack.us[/URL]
Thank-you for the help, I really appreciate it.
